# Changelog

## [0.4.0] - 2021-11-19

### Changed
- use error-container of libKitsunemimiCommon for error-output


## [0.3.2] - 2021-10-29

### Changed
- update requirements


## [0.3.1] - 2021-10-04

### Changed
- udpate from c++14 to c++17


## [0.3.0] - 2021-07-28

### Removed
- output-flag for buffer was removed to make it more flexible
- size-parameter of each array is not send by separate argument anymore

### Fixed
- kernel now waits until finished


## [0.2.0] - 2021-01-03

### Changed
- updated interface:
   - to identify buffer by a name instead of index, to make identification easier, when in comes to multiple kernels with multiple buffers
   - move objects into another class for cleaner code
- some internal restructures


## [0.1.0] - 2020-12-05

- first version
	- init device
	- copy data to device
	- run kernel
	- copy data from device
	- close device
	- get work-item information from device
	- get memory information from device
        - first support for multiple gpus and kernels

